English: Try to aspire to connect with people that will help you get to know other people within your career.
People need to understand that LinkedIn is not Facebook.
You're not there to make friends.
You're not going to use LinkedIn to post pictures.
You're using LinkedIn as a professional connection service to meet other individuals and connect with them from a business perspective.
Chinese: 努力追求与能帮你认识职场中其他人士的人建立联系。
人们需要明白领英并非脸书。
你去那里不是为了交朋友。
你不会用领英发布照片。
你是在利用领英这一专业人脉平台，从商业角度结识并连接他人。
